Font Licenses
==============

The PBF glyph files in this directory are sourced from the openmaptiles/fonts
project (https://github.com/openmaptiles/fonts) v2.0 release. Only the font
families used by this project's map styles are included.

Each font family retains its original license:

Noto Sans (Regular, Bold, Italic)
  License: SIL Open Font License 1.1 (OFL)
  Copyright: Google Inc.
  https://fonts.google.com/noto
  Free for commercial use. Must include this license notice.

Roboto (Regular, Medium, Condensed Italic)
  License: Apache License 2.0
  Copyright: Google Inc.
  https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Roboto
  Free for commercial use. Must include license notice.

Metropolis (Regular, Light, Light Italic, Medium Italic)
  License: Unlicense (Public Domain)
  Author: Chris Simpson
  https://fontsarena.com/metropolis-by-chris-simpson/
  Free for any use without restriction.

All fonts are compatible with MIT licensing and commercial use.
